T2 Design & Prototype - Product design & invention prototypes.








































 Industrial design and prototypes for inventions and new products

   

 











 Do you have an idea for a new product or invention? T2 Design & Prototype can help you create products from your invention ideas. Based in Los Angeles, California, T2 Design provides inventors with product design and development, prototypes, patent searching, market placement and manufacturing. T2 Design was featured building two prototypes on ABC’s hit TV show “American Inventor”, and has developed several products that have appeared on ABC’s “Shark Tank”, including Drop Stop invented by Marc Newburger and Jeffrey Simon and Reviver, invented by Ben Kusin.




   

   


